---
title: Karaage-Style Chicken Teriyaki with Sautéed Bok Choy and Rice
description: There's nothing like the sound of sizzling chicken to make your stomach rumble! Inspired by the Japanese style of karaage cooking, we've seasoned and coated juicy chicken tenders, then shallow fried them for crunchy, crispy goodness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-teriyaki-style-karaage-6a117d4b.jpg
